  </header>

  <p><strong>Grouped integrated labels</strong> place multiple floating-label inputs on a single row, balancing density with clarity. They’re ideal for compact auth forms or paired fields like URL + selector, letting related inputs stay visually connected while keeping each label discoverable.</p>

